<subSubSection id="C31AF981C1554A64C979F9309A3A684B" pageId="4" pageNumber="308" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="8BBFAA0AC1554A64C979F9309A3A684B" blockId="4.[102,1309,882,1941]" pageId="4" pageNumber="308">
<emphasis id="B9747618C1554A64C979F93099E069FA" bold="true" box="[105,457,1749,1782]" pageId="4" pageNumber="308">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. Endemic island rodents such as the Thick-spined Porcupine may be particularly at risk of extinction and require further study.
</paragraph>
